{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require pension & investment statements to include amount held in fossil fuels",
        "additional_details": "More people are now aware of the damage fossil fuels are doing to the planet, but many people aren't aware that their pensions/investments could be invested in fossil fuel companies. We want pension/ investment companies to disclose how much of an individual\u2019s investment is in fossil fuels. This will give individuals the chance to make an informed decision as to what they choose to invest their money in.",
        "background": "All pension and investment companies must be legally required to disclose how much of your money is invested in fossil fuel companies on annual statements and when you start a scheme.",
